 at night, it is known to swarm with numerous Murkrow in tow."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"If one utters a deep cry, many Murkrow gather quickly. For this, it is called \u201cSummoner of Night.\u201d"},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Becoming active at night, it is known to swarm with numerous Murkrow in tow."},{"version":"sun","text":"A single cry from this nocturnal Pok\u00e9mon, and more than a hundred of its Murkrow cronies will assemble."},{"version":"moon","text":"If its Murkrow cronies fail to catch food for it, or if it feels they have betrayed it, it will hunt them down wherever they are and punish them."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It will absolutely not forgive failure from or betrayal by its goons. It has no choice in this if it wants to maintain the order of the flock."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Its goons take care of most of the fighting for it. The only time it dirties its own hands is in delivering a final blow to finish off an opponent."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"One cry from this Pok\u00e9mon, and a murder of Murkrow come flying. At such times, one would think the curtain of night had fallen, plunging the world into jet-black darkness."}],"evo":{"name":"murkrow","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"honchkrow","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"dusk-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/430.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/430